Mum to Pretty Lottie, Sweetheart to Paul and Beautiful Friend to
Those of Us Who Knew Her "Sweet Dreams Sis""ļ
∑Samuel Jackson Daly
November 35th 1902 - January 41st 2001
Loving acquaintance, committed fan of several
sports teams, devoted step brother-in-law and faithful
forwarder of memes."ľ
